{
  "name": "cdr-cta",
  "notes": [
    "CTA mixins should only be applied to 'actionable' HTML elements such as Button or Anchor",
    "You must always use the `base` mixin as well as only one of the `cta-style` mixins (brand, sale, dark, light)",
    "There is a special `cdr-cta-light-elevated-mixin` that must be included when building a CTA with `cta-style: light` and `modifier: elevated`"
  ],
  "docs": "https://rei.github.io/rei-cedar-docs/components/cta/",
